### 1) Basic search without location
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "laptop"
}

### 2) Search with location (country only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "headphones",
  "location": {
    "country": "RO"
  }
}

### 3) Search with full location + example filters
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "coffee",
  "filters": {
    "maxPrice": 250,
    "fastDelivery": true
  },
  "location": {
    "country": "RO",
    "region": "Bucharest",
    "city": "Bucharest"
  }
}

### 4) Empty query (should not log saved search)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "",
  "location": {
    "country": "RO"
  }
}
